docker compose up # starts the data sources
npm run crawl # starts the crawler, indexes the data, gets 100 pages, embed them
npm run dev # starts the server on localhost:4000
curl 'localhost:4000/search?q="nouveau%20film"' # to try the search endpoint (add " | jq ." for formatting)

the projected was developped and tested using node v22.20.0

test coverage is minimal
error handling is minimal
